</div>  

**PingMe** is a modern, real-time chat application built with the **MERN stack** and powered by **WebSocket** for seamless communication. Designed with a sleek UI using **Chakra UI**, this app allows users to chat instantly in private or group conversations.  

👉 **[Live Demo](#)** | 📽 **[Demo Video](#)**  

---

## ✨ Features  

✅ **Real-time Messaging** – Instant chat powered by **WebSocket**  
✅ **User Authentication** – Secure login & signup with JWT  
✅ **Group Chats** – Create & join multiple chat rooms  
✅ **Responsive UI** – Beautiful & intuitive design with **Chakra UI**  
✅ **Emoji Support** – Express yourself with emojis 😊  
✅ **Online Status** – See who's active in real-time  
✅ **Message History** – Never lose your chats (MongoDB storage)  

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack  

| **Frontend**       | **Backend**        | **Database** | **Real-time** | **Styling**    |  
|--------------------|--------------------|--------------|---------------|----------------|  
| React.js           | Node.js            | MongoDB      | WebSocket     | Chakra UI      |  
| React Router       | Express.js         | Mongoose     | Socket.io     | CSS-in-JS      |  

